Source: skywarnplus-ng
Section: hamradio
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Jory A. Pratt <geekypenguin@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13),
               build-essential,
               python3 (>= 3.11),
               python3-pip,
               python3-venv,
               curl,
               ca-certificates
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/hardenedpenguin/SkywarnPlus-NG
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/hardenedpenguin/SkywarnPlus-NG
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/hardenedpenguin/SkywarnPlus-NG.git

Package: skywarnplus-ng
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: asl3-asterisk,
         asl3-tts,
         @LIBPYTHON_DEP@,
         ${misc:Depends},
         libsndfile1,
         ffmpeg,
         sox,
         curl,
         ca-certificates,
         wget
Recommends: apache2
Description: Weather alert system for Asterisk/app_rpt nodes
 SkywarnPlus-NG polls NWS alerts, drives voice announcements on Asterisk
 nodes, and provides a web dashboard. This package ships a prebuilt Python
 virtualenv so nodes do not download dependencies with pip at install time.
 .
 Target systems are AllStar Link 3 nodes with asl3-asterisk and asl3-tts.
 Voice synthesis uses the asl-tts CLI with Piper models in /var/lib/piper-tts.
